function gotresultsssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssssss(error, results)
{
    if(error)
    {
        console.error(error);
    }
    else
    {
        console.log(results);
        object = results;
    }
}

function draw()
{
    image(video, 0, 0, 640, 500);

    if( status != "")
    {
        for(var i = 0; i < object.length; i++)
        {
            document.getElementById("status").innerHTML = "Object detected";

            fill(255, 000, 000);
            percent = floor(object[i].confidence * 100);
            text(object[i].label + " " + percent + "%", object[i].x + 15, object[i].y + 15);
            noFill();
            stroke(255, 000, 000);
            rect(object[i].x, object[i].y, object[i].width, object[i].height);
            if(object[i].label != "person")
            {
                song.play();
                document.getElementById("found").innerHTML = "baby not found";
            }
            else
            {
                song.stop();
                document.getElementById("found").innerHTML = "baby found";
            }
        }
        if(object.length == 0)
        {
            song.play();
            document.getElementById("found").innerHTML = "baby not found";
        }
    }
    
}